      <title>澳大利亚政府向反对派提出澳联储改革方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/australian-treasurer-offers-opposition-rba-deal-to-pass-reforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚财政部长吉姆·查尔默斯表示，他已向自由国家党反对派提出对储备银行改革的让步，以确保其对立法改革的支持并结束长达数月的僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/australian-treasurer-offers-opposition-rba-deal-to-pass-reforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 00:33:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
